6.3 Ranking Logic

For query q:

Vectorize query

Compute similarity with all docs

Sort descending

Assign rank

6.4 Rank Stratification (CORE FEATURE)

From sorted list:

Top 20 → High relevance

Bottom 20 → Low relevance

Store:

{
  doc_id,
  rank,
  score,
  rank_group
}

